'''露易絲·瑪麗·理查德森女爵士''' ，[[大英帝國爵級司令勳章|DBE]]，[[愛丁堡皇家學會|FRSE]]（'''Dame Louise Mary Richardson'''，1958年6月8日-<ref name=whoswho/><ref name=Birth>{{cite web|title=Birthday's today|url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/archive/2011-6-8.html |publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=1 June 2014|date=8 June 2011|quote=Dr Louise Richardson, Principal and Vice–Chancellor, University of St Andrews, 53 }}</ref>）是一位愛爾蘭[[政治學家|政治學家]]，主要研究[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]<ref>{{YouTube|TxwNOZQZzLk|UCBerkeleyEvents, Conversations with History Video on ''What Terrorists Want''}}</ref>。2016年1月至今擔任[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]校長<ref>{{cite web|title = Vice-Chancellor {{!}} University of Oxford|url = http://www.ox.ac.uk/about/organisation/university-officers/vice-chancellor|website = www.ox.ac.uk|accessdate = 2016-01-04|archive-date = 2016-01-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160119083222/http://www.ox.ac.uk/about/organisation/university-officers/vice-chancellor|dead-url = no}}</ref>。此前為[[聖安德魯斯大學|聖安德魯斯大學]]校長，也是聖安德魯斯大學的第一位女校長。

==生平==
理查德森出生于[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]][[沃特福德郡|沃特福德郡]][[特拉莫爾|特拉莫爾]]，是亞瑟（Arthur）和朱莉·理查德森（Julie Richardson）夫婦七個子女中的一個<ref name=whoswho/><ref name=":0"/><ref name=":2">[http://www.wit.ie/about_wit/our_community/honorary_fellow_dr._louise_richardson "Honorary Fellow: Dr Louise Richardson"]. ''Waterford Institute of Technology''; retrieved 28 May 2015.</ref>。在家鄉讀完中學後前往[[都柏林三一學院|都柏林三一學院]]攻讀歷史本科，1982年在此基礎上獲得MA學位。<ref name=whoswho/> 1977年她前往[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]求學，1981年獲政治學碩士。后來又到[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]攻讀了國際關係和國際法的博士學位，此間研究[[馬島戰爭|馬島戰爭]]和[[蘇伊士危機|蘇伊士危機]]。<ref name=whoswho/><ref name=phd>{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Louise Mary|last=Richardson |title=Managing allies and being managed by alliances : Suez and the Falklands
 |publisher=Harvard University |date=1988 |url=http://id.lib.harvard.edu/aleph/002177658/catalog |oclc=23368823}}</ref>

1989至2001年間她在哈佛大學擔任助理教授和副教授<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/about/organisation/university-officers/vice-chancellor |title=Vice-Chancellor | University of Oxford |website=Ox.ac.uk |date=2016-01-01 |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-date=2016-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119083222/http://www.ox.ac.uk/about/organisation/university-officers/vice-chancellor |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[拉德克里夫高等研究院|拉德克里夫高等研究院]]院長，2009年成爲[[聖安德魯斯大學|聖安德魯斯大學]]校長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/principal/Installation|title=Installation of Principal and Vice-Chancellor|publisher=St-andrews.ac.uk|date=25 March 2009|accessdate=8 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530031103/http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/principal/installation/|archivedate=2015年5月30日}}</ref>，即是聖安德魯斯大學的第一位女校長和現代第一位信仰天主教的校長<ref name="NY Times Richardson">{{cite news|last=Bonner|first=Raymond|title=In Scotland, New Leadership Crumbles Old Barrier|publisher=New York Times|date=7 March 2009|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/03/28/world/europe/28richardson.html|accessdate=8 June 2015}}</ref>。2010年11月開始在該校擔任國際關係教授<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/administration/principalsoffice/members/principal |title=Archived copy |accessdate=June 8, 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150515022240/http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/administration/principalsoffice/members/principal/ |archivedate=May 15, 2015 }}</ref>。

2015年5月28日，[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]宣佈她將成為其下一任校長，她則在2016年1月1日上任。<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/news/2015-05-28-professor-louise-richardson-nominated-next-vice-chancellor|title=Professor Louise Richardson nominated as next Vice-Chancellor|publisher=University of Oxford|accessdate=2015-06-08}}</ref><ref name="VCapproval">{{cite news|url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2014-2015/25june2015-no5102/congregation/#209928|title=Declaration of approval of the appointment of a new Vice-Chancellor|work=[[Oxford_University_Gazette|Oxford University Gazette]]|publisher=[[University_of_Oxford|University of Oxford]]|date=25 June 2015|page=659|accessdate=28 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630002022/http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2014-2015/25june2015-no5102/congregation/#209928|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Guardian chancellor">{{cite web|last1=Adams|first1=Richard|title=Oxford vice-chancellor: ‘Tackling elitism can be done. I mean, I went to a rural school in Ireland’|url=http://www.theguardian.com/education/2016/jan/05/oxford-vice-chancellor-louise-richardson-university-admissions|website=The Guardian|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=6 January 2016}}</ref>
==争议==
她曾多次因薪水太高（年薪约41万镑）而招致批评<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/education/shortcuts/2017/sep/05/louise-richardson-oxford-410000-a-year-vice-chancellor|title=Why does Oxford’s £410,000-a-year vice-chancellor feel so hard done by?|work=The Guardian|access-date=2020-07-07|language=en-GB}}</ref>，此外她任上曾一年花去7万镑用来旅行和聚餐<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/2017/10/27/oxford-university-vice-chancellor-has-spent-70000-onexpenses/|title='Oxford University vice-Chancellor has spent £70,000 on expenses since taking up post last year, figures show'|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2020-07-07|language=en-GB}}</ref>。[[2019冠状病毒病英国疫情|2019冠状病毒病英国疫情]]期间，虽然整个牛津大学的员工工资都有所消减，但她的薪酬仍维持在原来的水平<ref>{{Cite news|title='Staff furloughed, top officials keep high salaries'|language=en-GB|work=Cherwell|url=https://cherwell.org/2020/05/02/staff-furloughed-top-officials-keep-high-salaries/|access-date=2020-07-07}}</ref>。

